headline: Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited (TSM) Widens Its Lead as AI Fuels Margin Expansion
summary: Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited (NYSE:TSM), or TSMC, is among Goldman Sachs’ top semiconductor stock picks. On January 16, Morgan Stanley lifted its price target on Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited (NYSE:TSM) to NT$2,088, a 5% increase. The investment bank also reiterated the stock as a top pick after the company reported strong quarterly results. […]
